Name: Run Star Motion CX Platform High Top
Description: ALL BLACK EVERYTHING Reflecting the energy of city streets, the Run Star Motion's playful and distorted lines are built for future movement. Reimagined from the inside out, the elevated stance and CX foam midsole help bring next-level comfort to every stride. The upper stays true to the original, juxtaposed by future-forward design details for bold self-expression. An exaggerated, wavy platform and sculptural traction lugs raise you up and help keep you steady with standout traction.

Description: YOU DESERVE IT New York City-based brand Alltimers mixes luxury vibes and back alley grit, giving anyone who rolls VIP status. For their first Converse CONS collaboration, the masters of irreverence brought their unique lens to the classic Fastbreak Pro. Bringing '90s court vibes and premium materials to the '83 original, the CONS Alltimers Fastbreak Pro features a premium leather and nubuck construction with added overlays and textures, inspired by Alltimers pro Alexis Sablone’s design prowess. Along with the lux execution, Alltimers added embossed branding to the heel and a printed sockliner. An aesthetic marvel with subtle nightlife nods, the CONS Alltimers Fastbreak Pro features a CX foam sockliner for impact cushioning and a traction rubber outsole for boardfeel and grip.

Description: YOU DESERVE IT NYC-based denizens of top-shelf irreverence bring '90s basketball aesthetics and lux materials to the classic One Star Pro for their first Converse CONS collaboration. Starting with a collegiate-inspired white, navy, and grey colorway, Alltimers transforms the One Star Pro into a guestlist-worthy silhouette with premium suede and nubuck upper with added overlays, embossed Alltimers branding, and a printed sockliner. Enhanced for skateboarding, the One Star Pro offers elastic tongue straps and a CX foam sockliner for lock-in fit and impact cushioning, and the traction rubber helps deliver flexible grip and boardfeel for skateboarding.

It features a slightly higher rubber foxing, a cushioned footbed that provides long-lasting comfort and a more substantial rubber toe cap. Additional vintage details include stitching on the sidewall and a heavier-grade canvas upper for comfort and durability. It’s an authentic throwback look that retains the iconic Chuck Taylor attributes you know and love, like the star-centered heel patch and vulcanized rubber outsole.

Converse x DRKSHDW TURBOWPN High Top
Description: OFF THE COURT. OUT OF PROPORTION. The punk-fueled collaboration with DRKSHDW transforms another court icon: the Converse Weapon. With a rebellious mindset to challenge the ubiquitous and break convention, Rick Owens exaggerates the proportions and distorts the lines of the legendary basketball sneaker. The result is a distinct design that sits at the intersection of hoops style and subversive fashion, bringing the edge of DRKSHDW boots to an iconic ‘80s basketball high top.

Converse x LFC Run Star Hike High Top
Description: THE CONVERSE x LIVERPOOL FC COLLECTION Converse and Liverpool FC come together in this limited-edition collection that celebrates the club’s history and champions its future. Inspired by the anthems sung on matchday, the Converse x LFC Run Star Hikes shiny upper is covered in "YNWA" (You'll Never Walk Alone) in cut-and-paste 'zine fashion' to pay tribute to Liverpool’s beating heart—its supporters. Style. Creativity. Art. This is Anfield.
